Romanization

Gieogsog-e ijhyeojyeo nachseol-eun geu pyojeong
Modu nal bius-eo amudo nal tteoolliji anhji

Ijen jichyeo sum-eul swil su eobs-eoseo
Mudgo sipji anh-a deoneun ib-eul ttel sudo eobsji

I need chains, rings
I need brush, lips
Nan wae wonhal sudo eobs-eo

I need hug, kiss
I need fame, praise
Nan wae wonhal su eobs-eo eojjaeseo?

Al-a anin geol (I don't know where to go)
Him-i eobsneun geol (I don't know what to say)
Gyeondil su eobs-eo (I don’t know how to do it, I don’t)
Dubadubadub

Ani eodideun (What used to be mine)
Yeogi anin gos (What used to belong)
Yeogsi tto dasi tto (What used to be love, It’s all gone)
Dubadubadub

