I need fame, praise
Nan wae wonhal su eobs-eo eojjaeseo?

Cheosjjae, naneun hangug-eseo taeeonaseo
Hangugmallo jalana geugeollo eum-ag-eul baewoga
Geunde yeogin gyeongjosa geum-aegdo nam-ui nunchiboneun
Nalayeoseo gyopo chingudeul-ui kulham-i

Buleowossdeon isibdaeleul gyeokkgo seumul huban-eulo
Eogjilo majchwogadeon eosbiseushamdeul sailo
Gwayeon nae eum-ag-eun eolmana jinsilhaess-eossneunji
Geutolog silh-eohadeon ttalajaeng-in anieoss-eossneunji

Duljjaeneun tagonajianh-assgo geuli jalnannom-i anieoseo
Haengbog-ilan heoul-eul eogjilo jabgo mwongal nohchigo sal-ass-eo
Jinjja ijeneun naega haengboghaejil chalye
Geunyang modeun geos-e namneunge jebal issgileul balae

Naleul wilohaji mal-a eochapi wilolan mal-en
Haedab-eun eobsji honja saghineun pyeon-i naa na-egen
Geunyang nal nae beolyeo dwo
Ani nae yaegil deul-eojwo

